ty and other characteristics of the occupants; and</li><li id="_d193281e-83a3-4b3d-ac05-c2d85136eee3">function or use of the structure.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_eef6fc15-2973-4a48-a9e9-766a300760ae" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_5a1fd168-60d5-474a-b2c1-b453638eda2c">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>So that occupants can safely evacuate a <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/2483_0.5.0.xml#_dcf88aaa-f959-470d-851a-80bf038bc603" id="_d6fcdfea-580f-446f-9556-0aa02f56c1f6" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">temporary structure</xref>, paths of travel to <xref xmlns:inv="urn:xpressauthor:xpressdocument" format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/5e2c1f63-e589-4ce1-95e8-5c3e286a7aff/1263_2.3.0.xml#_9712f630-8cf7-401b-b1cc-ae0be4485915" id="_1d8013d9-507e-4287-b37d-5319df6ad50b" inv:access="external" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">exits</xref> must have dimensions appropriate to the—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_8f09c9f8-0423-4b92-ba0a-36100f3b7f87">number, mobility and other characteristics of the occupants; and</li><li id="_ac5be124-0a6a-4493-b7f2-4534559ff498">function or use of the structure.</li></ol></subclause></clause>